       1  [MS-WMIO]:

     138   [MS-WMIO] – v20080207
     199  [MS-WMIO] – v20080207
     212  [MS-WMIO] – v20080207
     219      Instrumentation Remote Protocol, as specified in [MS-WMI], for network communication.
     222      Protocol (as specified in [MS-DCOM]) used in combination with Windows Management
     223      Instrumentation (WMI) (as specified in [MS-DCOM]) interfaces (as specified in [MS-WMI]). This
     225      in [MS-WMI]) operations, but specifies the data encoding used by the protocol.
     234      by the Windows Management Instrumentation Remote Protocol Specification (as specified in [MS-
     245      specified in [MS-WMI]) that transfers a CIM object MUST use the encoding within this specification.
     251      The following terms are defined in [MS-GLOS]:
     274      [MS-WMIO] – v20080207
     296   [MS-DCOM] Microsoft Corporation, "Distributed Component Object Model (DCOM) Remote Protocol
     299   [MS-GLOS] Microsoft Corporation, "Windows Protocols Master Glossary", March 2007.
     301   [MS-WMI] Microsoft Corporation, "Windows Management Instrumentation Remote Protocol
